{"tid":1551292,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"無冧巴防暴警開咪指混亂全因暴徒 警方3個月都保持冷靜","createTime":"2019-09-08T02:47:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T05:06:52.000Z","uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9ac3cbf24d98ef0a39661883e5e46162d3d5cd54","tid":1551292,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:47:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1341269659370307&amp;id=121625551334730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1341269659370307%26id%3D121625551334730&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprrJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=73c9a0b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1341269659370307&amp;id=121625551334730</a><br />\n<br />\n無冧巴防暴警開咪指混亂全因暴徒 警方3個月都保持冷靜<br />\n<br />\n有一批無有委任證的疑防暴警集結在東涌站出去對出空地，有市民要求出示委任證不果被無視。一名疑防暴警指「我哋警察喺過去3個月以嚟，已經保持冷靜嘅情緒」，並指市民要怪就怪責「暴徒」。<br />\n<br />\n#克警 #瘋警<br />\n#委任證呢<br />\n#到底咩叫冷靜<br />\n#907機場交通壓力測試<br />\n<br />\n現場報料：<a href=\"https://t.me/nextmaghk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fnextmaghk&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprrJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=4abe33d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/nextmaghk</a><br />\n----------<br />\n🌟講真心話 撐住我香港！🌟<br />\n9月2日起，每日$1 撐壹仔！<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2li67nA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2li67nA&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprrJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=042f598d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2li67nA</a>"},{"pid":"35d8f590a1c7a9f370f0e4172af5718e04369df9","tid":1551292,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:52:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fcd15bb69c7ab3aee0c48a3b17f08dfbe1c4fb5","tid":1551292,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:17:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\